<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Dama Korea privacy policy."><article class="article-shell legal-page"><h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p>Last updated: July 15, 2026</p><p>Dama Korea is committed to collecting as little personal information as practical. This policy explains what may be processed when you use damaheritage.com.</p><h2>Information you provide</h2><p>Dama Korea does not currently operate an email form or newsletter. Corrections submitted through the linked GitHub issue tracker are public and are processed under GitHub's own account and privacy terms. Do not submit identity documents or sensitive financial information.</p><h2>Analytics, cookies and advertising</h2><p>The site may use analytics and Google AdSense. These services may process device information, approximate location, browser data and interactions, and may use cookies or similar technologies subject to consent requirements in your region. Google explains how it uses information from sites that use its services in its published privacy documentation.</p><h2>Legal basis and choices</h2><p>Where applicable, processing may rely on consent, legitimate interests in operating and securing the site, or legal obligations. Browser controls and any consent interface offered on the site can be used to manage optional cookies.</p><h2>Retention and sharing</h2><p>Information is not sold. Service providers may process limited data to host, secure, measure or monetize the site.</p><h2>Questions</h2><p>General content corrections can be raised through the <a href="/contact/">public corrections page</a>. Do not use the public tracker to disclose personal information.</p></article></BaseLayout>
